thread.title: Jason Bermudez
thread.title_full: San Diego Self Storage reviewed by Jason Bermudez

author: Jason Bermudez
title: Jason Bermudez
text: I was referred by another customer at storage company. They had just what I wanted which was a drive up storage unit. They have the best prices in town. I appreciate that they have dollies and other services like a spare truck to use.
